        <h3 class='process-head'>Project Overview</h3>
        <p>
            Cheat Day is an app that serves as a simple way to be accountable for vices. 
            For certain active people, meal tracking and calorie counting micromanage too much, when sometimes just being aware of eating behaviors is enough. 
            Many people give themselves "cheat days" to eat unhealthy meals but generally have a healthy lifestyle. 
            This app would simply track and be a reminder to keep the healthy lifestyle. 
        </p>
        <p>
            While eating habits being the primary vice for the app, there would also be ways to add other vices (e.g. cigarettes, alcohol) to keep track of, as well.
        </p>
